# Runtime content installed/fetched into this door directory -- never
# committed. talkie/ and floppy/ are the freeware game data getdata.js
# downloads; scummvm is the deployed door binary (built by
# src/doors/syncscumm's build.sh, copied in by hand -- deploy tooling is a
# separate task); scummvm.ini is the per-directory reference config seeded
# from scummvm.example.ini by the installer's [copy:] step (an edited copy
# is a live config, not something to track here).
/talkie/
/floppy/
/syncscumm
/syncscumm.exe
/scummvm.ini
/*.log
